{"id":149502,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/美国中情局长称恐怖分子要对美国复仇/","date":"2011-05-03T01:00:24Z","modified":"2011-05-03T01:00:24Z","title":"美国中情局长称恐怖分子要对美国复仇","content":"<div>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">纽约</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美国中央情报局（</span><span>CIA</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）表示，基地组织将因本·拉登被杀对美国实行报复行动。美国中情局局长帕内塔（</span><span>Leon Panetta</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）在一份告中介绍说，恐怖分子</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">“</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">几乎可以肯定</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">”</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">会对美国进行报复。尽管本·拉登已经死了，但是基地组织并没有消亡。据德国总理默克尔估计，本·拉登被杀后德国的安全局势并不会有变化。但默克尔也表示，仍有必要保持警惕，国际恐怖主义的威胁还远未消除。</span></p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGltcHJlc3Npb24iLCAicHJvcGVydGllcyI6IHsidG9rZW4iOiAiYTRhNDYwYTM5MDRlZWU4ZmY1ZTAyNGVhNGJkZTdhYzIifX0=&#038;ip=1&#038;img=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /><a href=\"http://fulltextrssfeed.com\"><img src=\"http://fulltextrssfeed.com/images/1x1.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"ftrf - full text rss\" /></a><a href=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGNsaWNrIiwgInByb3BlcnRpZXMiOiB7InRva2VuIjogImE0YTQ2MGEzOTA0ZWVlOGZmNWUwMjRlYTRiZGU3YWMyIn19&#038;ip=1&#038;redirect=http://talkita.com/wrap?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw-world.de%2Fdw%2Farticle%2F0%2C%2C15044970%2C00.html%3Fmaca%3Dchi-rss-chi-all-1127-rdf&#038;title=%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E4%B8%AD%E6%83%85%E5%B1%80%E9%95%BF%E7%A7%B0%E6%81%90%E6%80%96%E5%88%86%E5%AD%90%E8%A6%81%E5%AF%B9%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E5%A4%8D%E4%BB%87\">Chat about this story w/ Talkita</a></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\">